title: Pavlyuchenkova ousts 2nd-seeded Safarova at Kremlin Cup
text: MOSCOW (AP) â€” Anastasia Pavlyuchenkova of Russia ousted second-seeded Lucie Safarova from the Kremlin Cup 6-1, 6-7 (2), 6-3 on Wednesday, leaving the Czech player vulnerable to being left out of the season-ending WTA finals.
